  "headline": "Dijkstra's Algorithm",
  "description": "Dijkstra (1956) finds shortest paths from a source vertex to all others in graphs with non-negative weights. O((V+E) log V) with binary heap. Does not work with negative weights — use Bellman-Ford.",
